This is a ruby class aimed to implement floating point arithmetic using only integer internals and bitwise operations.

This is done using IEEE 754 floating point standard.

### Currently supported

- Storage
- Addition

### Future work needed

- Subtraction
- Initialization from FixNum/Float/String types
- Multiplication
- Division
- Remainder
- ???

